<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5291&amp;p=47974#p47974"><![CDATA[
One scanline after the IRQ fires, IRQ is automatically acknowledged.<br />Or in other words, every scanline with frame on that doesn't trip the IRQ also acknowledges it.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Sat Jun 13, 2009 9:32 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
