<div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent"><br />Not planning on implementing ExRAM (yet), since it sounds like C3 doesn't use it. Does it use IRQs?<br /></div><br />Castlevania 3 use IRQs to show the status bar, and does a second scroll split for the second form of Death and the last 2 forms of Dracula. It <strong>does</strong> use EXRAM and IRQs in Aquarius level when the water is rising, the level is using the normal 2 nametables, while the water is from the third nametable in EXRAM. Other levels should be OK without EXRAM support though. It doesn't have WRAM on the board (altough I don't think it relies on open bus or anything like that).<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Thu Jun 11, 2009 11:14 am</p><hr />
